OL,5,G1000 Marcus Wareing: Tales from a..
OL,6,     FThis series follows Marcus - chef
OL,7,     Fextraordinaire and successful
OL,8,     Frestaurateur - as he follows his
OL,9,     Fdream of living, and cooking, in
OL,10,     Fthe English countryside.
OL,11,G1040 John & Lisa's Weekend Kitchen
OL,12,     FJohn Torode and Lisa Faulkner
OL,13,     Fprepare some Christmas dishes,
OL,14,     Fincluding ham in parsley sauce,
OL,15,     Fand curried puffs and potato
OL,16,     Fbombas, and share a recipe for
OL,17,     Ftraditional mincemeat.
